    ('3286', 'UserRegistrationCodeVerify', 'Email containing a verification code for new user registration.', 'Verification Code From UniBee', '<p>Dear&nbsp;user,</p>\n\n<p>Thank&nbsp;you&nbsp;for&nbsp;registering&nbsp;in&nbsp;UniBee.&nbsp;To&nbsp;ensure&nbsp;the&nbsp;security&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;account,&nbsp;we&nbsp;need&nbsp;to&nbsp;verify&nbsp;your&nbsp;email,&nbsp;please&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;verification&nbsp;code&nbsp;below:</p>\n\n<p>Your&nbsp;Verification&nbsp;Code:&nbsp;{Code}</p>\n\n<p>Notes:</p>\n\n<p>This&nbsp;code&nbsp;is&nbsp;valid&nbsp;for&nbsp;{CodeExpireMinute}&nbsp;&nbsp;minutes.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Please&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;share&nbsp;this&nbsp;code&nbsp;with&nbsp;anyone.</p>\n\n<p>Thanks,</p>\n\n<p>UniBee&nbsp;Team&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 17:33:35', '2025-07-22 07:39:10', '0', NULL),
    ('3287', 'UserOTPLogin', 'Email providing a one-time verification code (OTP) for secure user login.', 'Your One-Time Code for Secure Login to UniBee', '<p>Hi&nbsp;{User&nbsp;name},</p>\n\n<p>To&nbsp;ensure&nbsp;the&nbsp;secure&nbsp;login&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;account&nbsp;in&nbsp;UniBee,&nbsp;we&nbsp;have&nbsp;generated&nbsp;a&nbsp;One-Time&nbsp;Password&nbsp;(OTP)&nbsp;for&nbsp;your&nbsp;login&nbsp;attempt.&nbsp;Please&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;following&nbsp;OTP&nbsp;to&nbsp;access&nbsp;your&nbsp;account:</p>\n\n<p>Your&nbsp;One-Time&nbsp;Code:&nbsp;{Code}</p>\n\n<p>Notes:</p>\n\n<p>This&nbsp;code&nbsp;is&nbsp;valid&nbsp;for&nbsp;{CodeExpireMinute}&nbsp;minutes.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Please&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;share&nbsp;this&nbsp;OTP&nbsp;with&nbsp;anyone.</p>\n\n<p>If&nbsp;you&nbsp;did&nbsp;not&nbsp;initiate&nbsp;this&nbsp;login&nbsp;attempt,&nbsp;please&nbsp;ignore&nbsp;this&nbsp;email.</p>\n\n<p>If&nbsp;you&nbsp;have&nbsp;any&nbsp;other&nbsp;question,&nbsp;please&nbsp;contact&nbsp;the&nbsp;support&nbsp;team.</p>\n\n<p>Cheers!</p>\n\n<p>UniBee&nbsp;Team&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 17:41:23', '2025-07-22 07:42:20', '0', NULL),
    ('3288', 'SubscriptionCancelledAtPeriodEndByMerchantAdmin', 'Notification to user about subscription cancellation by merchant admin at period end.', 'Your Subscription Will Cancelled At {PeriodEnd} By {Merchant Name}', '<p>Hi&nbsp;{User&nbsp;name},</p>\n\n<p>This&nbsp;email&nbsp;is&nbsp;to&nbsp;confirm&nbsp;your&nbsp;recent&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;cancellation.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Your&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;will&nbsp;remain&nbsp;active&nbsp;until&nbsp;{PeriodEnd}.</p>\n\n<p>After&nbsp;{PeriodEnd},&nbsp;your&nbsp;{Merchant&nbsp;Product&nbsp;Name}&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;terminated&nbsp;and&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;not&nbsp;be&nbsp;able&nbsp;to&nbsp;continue&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;service.</p>\n\n<p>If&nbsp;you&nbsp;decide&nbsp;to&nbsp;continue&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;service,&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;renew&nbsp;the&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;at&nbsp;any&nbsp;time&nbsp;by&nbsp;navigating&nbsp;to&nbsp;your&nbsp;billing&nbsp;dashboard,&nbsp;clicking&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Subscription”&nbsp;tab&nbsp;and&nbsp;selecting&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;plan.</p>\n\n<p>In&nbsp;case&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;questions,&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;hesitate&nbsp;to&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;-&nbsp;{Merchant’s&nbsp;customer&nbsp;support&nbsp;email&nbsp;address}.</p>\n\n<p>Important:&nbsp;do&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;reply&nbsp;to&nbsp;this&nbsp;email,&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;contact&nbsp;mentioned&nbsp;above&nbsp;instead.</p>\n\n<p>Warm&nbsp;regards,</p>\n\n<p>{Merchant&nbsp;Name}</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 17:55:16', '2025-07-22 07:39:11', '0', NULL),
    ('3289', 'SubscriptionCancelledAtPeriodEndByUser', 'Confirmation to user about self-initiated subscription cancellation at period end.', 'We Received Your Cancellation Request', '<p>Hi&nbsp;{User&nbsp;name},</p>\n\n<p>This&nbsp;email&nbsp;is&nbsp;to&nbsp;confirm&nbsp;your&nbsp;recent&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;cancellation.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Your&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;will&nbsp;remain&nbsp;active&nbsp;until&nbsp;{PeriodEnd}.</p>\n\n<p>After&nbsp;{PeriodEnd},&nbsp;your&nbsp;{Merchant&nbsp;Product&nbsp;Name}&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;terminated&nbsp;and&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;not&nbsp;be&nbsp;able&nbsp;to&nbsp;continue&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;service.</p>\n\n<p>If&nbsp;you&nbsp;decide&nbsp;to&nbsp;continue&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;service,&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;renew&nbsp;the&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;at&nbsp;any&nbsp;time&nbsp;by&nbsp;navigating&nbsp;to&nbsp;your&nbsp;billing&nbsp;dashboard,&nbsp;clicking&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Subscription”&nbsp;tab&nbsp;and&nbsp;selecting&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;plan.</p>\n\n<p>In&nbsp;case&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;questions,&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;hesitate&nbsp;to&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;-&nbsp;{Merchant’s&nbsp;customer&nbsp;support&nbsp;email&nbsp;address}.</p>\n\n<p>Important:&nbsp;do&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;reply&nbsp;to&nbsp;this&nbsp;email,&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;contact&nbsp;mentioned&nbsp;above&nbsp;instead.</p>\n\n<p>Warm&nbsp;regards,</p>\n\n<p>{Merchant&nbsp;Name}</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 17:55:16', '2025-07-22 07:39:11', '0', NULL),
    ('3290', 'NewProcessingInvoice', 'Notification about a new invoice generated for subscription payment.', 'New Invoice from {Merchant Product Name}', '<p>Hi,&nbsp;{User&nbsp;name}!&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We&nbsp;hope&nbsp;this&nbsp;message&nbsp;finds&nbsp;you&nbsp;well.&nbsp;We&nbsp;are&nbsp;writing&nbsp;to&nbsp;inform&nbsp;you&nbsp;that&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;invoice&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;generated&nbsp;for&nbsp;your&nbsp;{Merchant&nbsp;Product&nbsp;Name}&nbsp;subscription.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Please&nbsp;click&nbsp;the&nbsp;following&nbsp;link&nbsp;and&nbsp;process&nbsp;the&nbsp;payment:&nbsp;{Link}</p>\n\n<p>The&nbsp;invoice&nbsp;needs&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;paid&nbsp;before&nbsp;the&nbsp;due&nbsp;date&nbsp;{PeriodEnd}&nbsp;to&nbsp;avoid&nbsp;possible&nbsp;interruptions&nbsp;while&nbsp;working&nbsp;with&nbsp;{Merchant&nbsp;Product&nbsp;Name}.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In&nbsp;case&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;questions,&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;hesitate&nbsp;to&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;-&nbsp;{Merchant’s&nbsp;customer&nbsp;support&nbsp;email&nbsp;address}.</p>\n\n<p>Important:&nbsp;do&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;reply&nbsp;to&nbsp;this&nbsp;email,&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;contact&nbsp;mentioned&nbsp;above&nbsp;instead.</p>\n\n<p>Thank&nbsp;you,</p>\n\n<p>{Merchant&nbsp;Name}</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 16:20:10', '2025-07-22 07:39:11', '0', NULL),
