    ('3296', 'SubscriptionNeedAuthorized', 'Notification to user about a payment issue requiring authorization for subscription.', 'Action Required - Payment Issue for Your {Merchant Product Name} Subscription', '<p>Hi,&nbsp;{User&nbsp;name}!&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We&nbsp;recently&nbsp;attempted&nbsp;to&nbsp;process&nbsp;the&nbsp;payment&nbsp;for&nbsp;your&nbsp;{Merchant&nbsp;Product&nbsp;Name}&nbsp;but&nbsp;encountered&nbsp;an&nbsp;issue.&nbsp;Unfortunately,&nbsp;we&nbsp;were&nbsp;unable&nbsp;to&nbsp;charge&nbsp;the&nbsp;amount&nbsp;of&nbsp;&nbsp;{Payment&nbsp;Amount}&nbsp;{Currency}&nbsp;to&nbsp;your&nbsp;account.</p>\n\n<p>Here&#39;s&nbsp;how&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;try&nbsp;to&nbsp;resolve&nbsp;this&nbsp;issue:</p>\n\n<p>1.&nbsp;Check&nbsp;Payment&nbsp;Details:</p>\n\n<p>Ensure&nbsp;that&nbsp;your&nbsp;payment&nbsp;details&nbsp;are&nbsp;up-to-date&nbsp;and&nbsp;correct.&nbsp;You&nbsp;can&nbsp;review&nbsp;and&nbsp;update&nbsp;this&nbsp;information&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;billing&nbsp;dashboard&nbsp;under&nbsp;the&nbsp;“Billing&nbsp;details”&nbsp;tab.</p>\n\n<p>2.&nbsp;Verify&nbsp;Funds:</p>\n\n<p>Confirm&nbsp;that&nbsp;there&nbsp;are&nbsp;sufficient&nbsp;funds&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;account&nbsp;to&nbsp;cover&nbsp;the&nbsp;subscription&nbsp;cost.</p>\n\n<p>3.&nbsp;Card&nbsp;Requirements:</p>\n\n<p>If&nbsp;you&#39;re&nbsp;using&nbsp;a&nbsp;card,&nbsp;please&nbsp;make&nbsp;sure&nbsp;it&nbsp;supports&nbsp;3D&nbsp;Secure,&nbsp;as&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;required&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;secure&nbsp;transaction.</p>\n\n<p>4.&nbsp;Try&nbsp;Alternative&nbsp;Payment&nbsp;Options:</p>\n\n<p>Consider&nbsp;using&nbsp;cryptocurrencies&nbsp;or&nbsp;other&nbsp;methods&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;payment.</p>\n\n<p>Please&nbsp;log&nbsp;in&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;billing&nbsp;system&nbsp;and&nbsp;give&nbsp;it&nbsp;a&nbsp;try.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In&nbsp;case&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;questions,&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;ever&nbsp;hesitate&nbsp;to&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;-&nbsp;{Merchant’s&nbsp;customer&nbsp;support&nbsp;email&nbsp;address}.</p>\n\n<p>Important:&nbsp;do&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;reply&nbsp;to&nbsp;this&nbsp;email,&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;contact&nbsp;mentioned&nbsp;above&nbsp;instead.</p>\n\n<p>Best&nbsp;regard,</p>\n\n<p>{Merchant&nbsp;Name}</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 17:55:16', '2025-07-22 07:39:14', '0', NULL),
    ('3297', 'InvoiceRefundCreated', 'Notification to user that a refund has been initiated for a payment.', 'Your Payment for {Merchant Product Name} has process a Refund', '<p>We&nbsp;have&nbsp;processed&nbsp;a&nbsp;refund&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;amount&nbsp;of&nbsp;{Refund&nbsp;Amount}&nbsp;{Currency}.</p>\n\n<p>The&nbsp;refund&nbsp;should&nbsp;reach&nbsp;your&nbsp;account&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;next&nbsp;3-7&nbsp;business&nbsp;days.&nbsp;-&nbsp;depends&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;Merchant’s&nbsp;policy&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In&nbsp;case&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;questions,&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;ever&nbsp;hesitate&nbsp;to&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;-&nbsp;{Merchant’s&nbsp;customer&nbsp;support&nbsp;email&nbsp;address}.</p>\n\n<p>Important:&nbsp;do&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;reply&nbsp;to&nbsp;this&nbsp;email,&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;contact&nbsp;mentioned&nbsp;above&nbsp;instead.</p>\n\n<p>Best&nbsp;regard,</p>\n\n<p>{Merchant&nbsp;Name}</p>', NULL, '2024-01-25 17:55:16', '2025-07-22 07:39:14', '0', NULL),
